  "page": "Lady Stork",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lady Stork</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_(playhouse)\" title=\"Gate (playhouse)\">Gate</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nEssie Davis</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">Season 6</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lady Stork</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummer</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. She is part of the mummer's troupe at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_(playhouse)\" title=\"Gate (playhouse)\">Gate</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, she is renamed <b>Lady Crane</b> and is portrayed by Essie Davis.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lady_Stork&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lady Stork likes to have <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> before each performance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lady_Stork&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lady_Stork&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady Stork steps on the hem of her gown before <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Bloody_Hand\" title=\"The Bloody Hand\">The Bloody Hand</a></i> begins, so <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Mercy</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daena_(mummer)\" title=\"Daena (mummer)\">Daena</a> sew it up.  Mercy pours Lady Stork a little nip of <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> before the play begins.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lady_Stork&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-winds-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, Mercy</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404085424\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.125 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.581 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 416/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2395/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6935/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 845/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 648/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.310/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  557.950      1 -total\n 98.44%  549.265      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.86%  546.017      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.83%   60.440     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.63%   20.261      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  0.53%    2.975      1 Templa